{"type": "article", "id": 24367, "title": "带星点的金属凳子", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-24T07:00:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 12, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607104134HurjCJs80Rw2zFM6.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一把由金属制作的凳子，它的造型非常简单，有点像倒扣起来的桶，似乎可以感受到凳子旋转起来的轻盈。在凳子的最上面有一圈凹进去的纹路，突出了座位的特征。整体喷上了细密的圆点，有黑与白、绿与粉这类反差较大的对比，色彩跳跃而有活力，也有蓝和白、粉和白这样较清新的搭配，都很有个性，是英国设计师为家具品牌 Hem 设计，目前还没有上市。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104132tya9fuJlT2iwo43v.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104132okBi7AlnrpeObTtG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.09508547\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104133jU5ipfzYluqWA2DR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.14529915\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104133KoPX2mujFMR6ZwCn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.99893162\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}